<view class="pb">
  <lz-header title="更换手机号" />

  <view class="lz-page" style="padding-bottom: 40px;">
    <view class="pb__hero">
      <view class="pb__hero-icon"><lz-icon name="phone" size="26" color="accent" stroke="2" /></view>
      <view class="pb__hero-phone">{{maskedPhone}}</view>
      <view class="pb__hero-tip">当前绑定的登录手机号</view>
    </view>

    <view class="lz-card pb__info">
      <lz-icon name="info" size="18" color="accent" />
      <text>如需更换登录手机号，请联系管理员核实身份后为您处理，以保障账号与经营数据安全。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="lz-section-label" style="margin-top: var(--gap);">温馨提示</view>
    <view class="lz-card lz-card--flush">
      <view class="lz-row">
        <view class="lz-row__icon"><lz-icon name="shield" size="17" color="accent" /></view>
        <view class="lz-row__main"><view class="lz-row__label" style="font-size:14px;">更换后原手机号将无法登录</view></view>
      </view>
      <view class="lz-row lz-row--last">
        <view class="lz-row__icon"><lz-icon name="check" size="17" color="accent" /></view>
        <view class="lz-row__main"><view class="lz-row__label" style="font-size:14px;">账号数据不受影响，完整保留</view></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="lz-footer">
    <button class="lz-btn lz-btn--primary lz-btn--lg lz-btn--full" bindtap="onContact">
      <lz-icon name="message" size="20" color="white" /> 联系管理员
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
